straight home.

00:03:35,548 --> 00:03:37,149
BRASS:
Where do you work?

00:03:37,216 --> 00:03:38,784
At the feed lot off Highway 111.

00:03:38,851 --> 00:03:40,419
I've got a Masters
in English Literature.

00:03:40,486 --> 00:03:41,820
I used to teach high school.

00:03:41,887 --> 00:03:44,423
Let me guess--
the kids loved you.

00:03:44,490 --> 00:03:46,792
