girl went missing.

00:04:00,439 --> 00:04:02,775
Hamilton... he barely
finished high school.

00:04:02,841 --> 00:04:05,344
He has a lot of displaced anger.

00:04:05,411 --> 00:04:06,612
Hmm.

00:04:06,679 --> 00:04:08,914
