sexual predators.

00:04:47,019 --> 00:04:48,721
Ask my parole
officer.

00:04:48,787 --> 00:04:50,489
Doesn't that count
for something?

00:04:52,124 --> 00:04:54,093
I don't know.

00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:57,329
But it doesn't change anything,
does it?

00:04:57,396 --> 00:04:59,765
WOMAN (on TV):
<i>Police have no new clues</i>

00:04:59,832 --> 00:05:01,000
